      "fieldId": "1a000003-0000-4000-a000-000000000003",
      "value": "`RepositoryManifest.container` is the canonical `Container` for the repository. It must satisfy all core Container invariants (Invariants 20–21). If a separate `container.json` is present in the repository root, it must be consistent with the manifest's embedded Container; the manifest takes precedence on conflict."
